snippet.textDisplay:
I'll toss in my own:
1. Ciabatta cut horizontally and lightly toasted on a grill.
2. Tzatziki spread on both the top and bottom buns of the ciabatta (alternatively use Guacamole, also very good)
3. Iceberg lettuce.
4. Chicken breast butterflied, marinated in salt, pepper, paprika, and soy sauce and grilled or pan-fried.
5. Gauda 1-2 layer(s) of gouda cheese.
6. Cherry tomatoes sliced thin.
7. Close the sandwich with the top ciabatta bun.
8. Discover heaven.
